              Find exactly what you're looking for with our <strong>multi-dimensional filtering system</strong>. 
              Filter by discipline, time period, keywords, authors, and citation count.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-arxiv-gray-100 dark:bg-arxiv-gray-100 p-3 rounded-sm">
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black mb-1">Filter Options:</div>
              <ul class="text-sm text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black space-y-1">
                <li>• 6 major disciplines + 100+ subcategories</li>
                <li>• Custom date ranges and time periods</li>
                <li>• Author and institution filtering</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Export & Share -->
          <div class="border-2 border-arxiv-black dark:border-arxiv-black p-8 bg-arxiv-white dark:bg-arxiv-white hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-arxiv-red dark:bg-arxiv-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-download text-2xl text-arxiv-white dark:text-arxiv-white"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black mb-4 font-sans">Export & Share</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Share your discoveries with colleagues and collaborators. Export visualizations in <strong>multiple formats</strong> 
              and generate comprehensive reports for presentations and publications.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-arxiv-gray-100 dark:bg-arxiv-gray-100 p-3 rounded-sm">
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black mb-1">Export Formats:</div>
              <ul class="text-sm text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black space-y-1">
                <li>• High-res PNG, SVG, PDF</li>
                <li>• Interactive HTML reports</li>
                <li>• Raw data in CSV, JSON</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Collaborative Features -->
          <div class="border-2 border-arxiv-black dark:border-arxiv-black p-8 bg-arxiv-white dark:bg-arxiv-white hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-arxiv-gray dark:bg-arxiv-gray rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-users text-2xl text-arxiv-white dark:text-arxiv-white"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black mb-4 font-sans">Collaborative Research</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Work together with your research team. <strong>Share insights, annotate findings</strong>, 
              and collaborate on trend analysis with built-in commenting and sharing features.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-arxiv-gray-100 dark:bg-arxiv-gray-100 p-3 rounded-sm">
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black mb-1">Collaboration Tools:</div>
              <ul class="text-sm text-arxiv-black dark:text-arxiv-black space-y-1">
                <li>• Team workspaces and projects</li>
                <li>• Annotation and commenting system</li>
                <li>• Real-time collaborative editing</li>
              </ul>
